Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think this would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose, not to the likes of you, Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:56.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Last year, my determination to beat\NOchi was what let me get back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:00.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,after losing three straight games\Nto Shindou, Waya, and Fuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,"My Go is supporting me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,"I'll believe in my own strength."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was able to tell myself that back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:17.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But will I be able to say the same thing\Nhere in the Chinese Go Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Will my Go support me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:28.13,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(340,115)}The Sixty-Seventh Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:28.13,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Isumi Tested
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Don't lose courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:35.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I go to Japan from here without confidence,\NI won't stand a chance in the pro exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:42.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Waya, Shindou, Ochi... I won't be able\Nto look them in the eye again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Phone call? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.44,Background,,0,0,0,,Shinichirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Call us if you're going to stay in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:04.16,Background,,0,0,0,,The only reason we weren't panicking\Nwas because Sakurano-san called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, there was a lot going on, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.22,Background,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you want to do it, but...\Nhow long are you going to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Sakurano-san said three or four days, is she right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.99,Background,,0,0,0,,Shinichirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here until the pro exam starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.68,Background,,0,0,0,,Two months!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:37.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I don't lose confidence here, but instead gain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to face the pro exams...\Nmaybe even the world of the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai-san, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I wouldn't earlier but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you. I won't be troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.57,Background,,0,0,0,,You have a Go board in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:20.57,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came here instead of going to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.25,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to study at night if there's\Na Go board in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. You really are studious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave the Go board out, so\Nuse it to replay games or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.82,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll just be fiddling with my computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.29,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, do you use computers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Two months is my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you play anyone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I played a child called Le Ping and... I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!? You lost to him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a league match, with an\Nhour and a half on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping laughed mockingly at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. You should have crushed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed at you mockingly? That brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down. We're playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but if you can't even beat Le\NPing, I can't let you stay in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me leave? Yang Hai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, place two stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's 7:30 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.03,Background,,0,0,0,,You can use whatever's around, Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sleeping, go on ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's about as strong as Le Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He has a lot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:34.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He never told me to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess he accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:44.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The game I played against Yang Hai-san last night\Nwith two stones, was not played for win or loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It was a tutoring game from a top class player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.55,Background,,0,0,0,,I saw you played Wang Xing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Hua Song Li-san joined in for the\Ndiscussion afterwards. I was amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're top players in China,\Neven I had heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them came back from a match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The top pros in China sure are young,\Nit's not like Japan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the younger players start dragging\Nyou down by the time you're past thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're over if you don't\Nwork hard during your teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Le Ping...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.89,Background,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do tonight? Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's a day off. So I'll play against\Nyou for however long you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.92,Background,,0,0,0,,Li Lao Shi isn't around on the days off,\Nand not many people are playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao-kun! You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:13.97,Background,,0,0,0,,I stayed here. I wanted to play\Nyou again, so I stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.23,Background,,0,0,0,,Zhao Shi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your match?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside! Let's go bowling! Bowling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun? He's studying here\Nfor a while, but he sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He sucks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I played him and I owned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:45.19,Background,,0,0,0,,He can't beat me no matter\Nhow much he studies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.51,Background,,0,0,0,,I can't let that comment go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping, try playing Isumi-kun again.\NThis time your going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing with Zhao today because\Nwe have the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You play enough during the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yang Hai Xian Sheng, all you\Ndo is play on your computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.15,Background,,0,0,0,,Never mind what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if I play Isumi-kun again and beat\Nhim, will you stop yelling at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but if you lose to Isumi-kun,\Nbe more studious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Zhao Shi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have the match in a week. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.39,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fscy120\1c&H516163&\bord0\shad0\frz346\pos(332,187)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.18,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Nase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you haven't been going to the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.54,Background,,0,0,0,,Le Ping and I both came from Yun'an province.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to Yun'an province for a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,both of Le Ping's parents asked\Nme how Le Ping was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:33.70,Background,,0,0,0,,They were quite worried as to how\Ntheir only precious son was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With his current grades, he's going to get\Nsent back to the provinces next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, teach him a lesson\Nso that he'll start studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.27,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for using you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I have to thank Le Ping then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him you're playing\Nagainst me every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that gives me all the more reason to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! I set up the match because\NI thought you could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,On a different note, how did the\Ngame you lost to him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:24.39,Background,,0,0,0,,I lost to Zhao the day before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.92,Background,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was too determined not to lose\Nagainst a small child twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to play like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to pretend that the game\Nwas part of the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of improving my game,\Nit just made me too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your pro exams go last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:52.82,Background,,0,0,0,,I was bothered by something someone else said,\Nand I made a great mistake during a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.95,Background,,0,0,0,,I lost track of myself, and it took some time\Nbefore I was able to get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:00.28,Background,,0,0,0,,And the three losses I had in the\Nmeantime caused me to fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bad at controlling your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about what the people around you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Irritation, eagerness, worry, aggression, tension,\Npressure. Don't let these emotions control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Thats the most important lesson for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at the stones. You can do this\Nwith practice and determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:30.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Your personality doesn't matter.\NThis is a skill that you can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A skill that I can learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I had never thought of it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can learn to control my emotions!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have a great weapon in your arsenal\Nonce you learn how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Huh? Game between Le Ping and Isumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.59,Background,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai Xian Sheng is training Isumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:08.23,Background,,0,0,0,,Who said that Isumi-kun sucked? I played\Nhim and I think he's better than Le Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.85,Background,,0,0,0,,He's started to calm down lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.36,Background,,0,0,0,,He seemed a little nervous before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Cheng Yi lost to Isumi-kun in a league match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.75,Background,,0,0,0,,It's time already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! I would be at the arcade already\Nif it wasn't for this stupid match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is late, what is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.88,Background,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai Xian Sheng said that the\Nmatch would be at around 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to be late for the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine. It starts around 1:40 so let's\Nrelax and go at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.44,Background,,0,0,0,,There's no risk at all to you in\Ntoday's game, so take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I can't look you in the\Nface if I lose, Yang Hai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.87,Background,,0,0,0,,If that were to happen, I wouldn't\Nfeel comfortable staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I wouldn't feel comfortable staying\Nin the Chinese Go Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to go back to Japan feeling\Nwretched about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You don't have to pressure\Nyourself that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I have. I can look at myself from\Nthe third person despite that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:34.65,Background,,0,0,0,,When I create another personality\Ninside me, I start to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late! It's already 1:40!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I only said "around" 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun, let's have a private conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I talk to you in Japanese, Le Ping might\Nthink that I'm telling you a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:05.47,Background,,0,0,0,,And I told him to come here 10 minutes before the\Nmatch starts, so he's angry at having to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how emotions can\Naffect your game play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang Hai-san! Never do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:23.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh crap! Isumi-kun's a serious guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I was late. I'll take twice the amount\Nof time I was late away from my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:39.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What good does it do for me to\Nmake Isumi-kun emotional!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm an idiot! An idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Yang Hai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:09.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Man, not only does he get here\Nlate, he's playing really slow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!? Don't waste\Nso much time on your first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You don't have that much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:35.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll have to apologize to Isumi-kun\Nif he loses because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:46.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's not that I didn't have faith in Isumi-kun...\Nit's that I wanted some insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's still some weakness in White's\Nterritory on the lower right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun is preparing so that\Nhe can make an attack on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Le Ping would have to cover his stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Isumi-kun's move was quite powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The section proceeded just as I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:18:01.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun was always calm when playing against\Nme, no matter how much trouble he was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:07.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So, he can always play a game like this so long as he plays calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:19.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He played a move that I didn't expect. That's\Na great Tesuji for the end game, Le Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:34.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Though it is a skill you can learn, it will\Ntake him some time to master it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But it seems like he has gotten past a major obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.18,Background,,0,0,0,,Game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun wins by two and a half moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:55.48,Background,,0,0,0,,I was panicking because of what you\Ndid before the game, Yang Hai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you played calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-kun! One more game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many games of 10 second\NGo did you think we played?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's upset that you're about even.\NHe wants to be better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, looks like there was no need for me\Nto tell him to be more studious if he lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected Le Ping to drag\NIsumi-kun to the game room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be gone for a bit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.73,Background,,0,0,0,,You're playing Zhao next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:40.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Zhao's idol strap is mine if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lose he gets my MD player.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:54.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Le Ping's been clinging onto Isumi-kun,\Nand studying Go a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.93,Background,,0,0,0,,He was probably urged on by looking\Nat Isumi-kun's motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to thank Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very glad that he didn't leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.23,Background,,0,0,0,,Hello? Dad? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you apply for the pro exam for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be home a week before the pro exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With confidence to walk bravely into\Nit... no, into the world of the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:37.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes! To the world that everyone\Nhas been in for a year now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:12.32,umezawa61,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\an5\1a&HFF&\pos(415,54)\4c&HF5AC43&\4a&HFF&\shad1.1\t(0,112,1,\1a&H00&\4a&H50&)}U
