Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do "Under the Stone" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:18.11,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(250,0)\3c&H058909&\4c&H058909&\fscx100\fscy80\bord1\shad0.5\move(780,367,281,367)}Black First, Black Lives
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:20.26,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H058909&\4c&H058909&\fscx100\fscy80\bord1\shad0.5\pos(281,367)}Black First, Black Lives
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.20,Background,,0,0,0,,Black lives if Black goes first here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try, Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:27.69,Background,,0,0,0,,If I take these four stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:29.61,Background,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:34.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup, now Black can take these two stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:41.52,Background,,0,0,0,,So Black now has two eyes, and his life. This\Nis the right Tesuji for Under the Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:46.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Had you connected here, White\Nwould have played here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.88,Background,,0,0,0,,this is a deficient eye and Black would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Under the Stone" is a Tesuji that\Nappears frequently in real games.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:54.92,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs23\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(334,334)\3c&H058909&\4c&H058909&\fscx99\fscy105\bord1\shad0.5\pos(318,378)}Learn "Under the Stone" and use it in a real match{\i1}!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take this opportunity to learn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:55.48,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(83,0)\3c&H1400EF&\4c&H1400EF&\fscx99\fscy100\bord1\shad0.5\move(303,260,303,308)}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.37,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H1400EF&\4c&H1400EF&\fscx99\fscy100\bord1\shad0.5\pos(303,308)}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:58.77,Background,,0,0,0,,Quit being a pro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:00.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:04.07,Background,,0,0,0,,This is so annoying! What is he doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're not playing any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to quit being a pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll guess I'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:12.29,Background,,0,0,0,,There's no point in being a genius if you don't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:26.38,Background,,0,0,0,,I can't want to play!
